<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #d32f2f;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 32px;
      color: #333333;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #c62828;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .stake-details {
      background-color: #ffebee;
      border-left: 5px solid #d32f2f;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .stake-details p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #555555;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #d32f2f;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888888;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>FundedUp Admin</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>New challenge is Pending Approval</h2>
      <p>Hello Admin,</p>
      <p>A new Trading Challenge has been submitted and is awaiting your approval. Please review the details below.</p>
      
      <div class="stake-details">
        <p>Staker: <strong>{{stakerName}}</strong></p>
        <p>Amount: <strong>{{amount}}$</strong></p>
      </div>
      
      <p>To approve or reject this challenge, please login to admin dashboard and navigate to the stake approval panel.</p>
      
      
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 FundedUp. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>